{
  "stem": "26486.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they stopped us in front of the Gestapo cause a-- we were kind of afraid anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We said-- trying to make believe they're going to be nice, but we have no-- no faith in them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, they stopped us in front of the lake, and the crematorium was right in front of the lake.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we said, gee, maybe they're going to stick us here in the crematorium alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did-- they did that with others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We weren't surprised, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So Lil said, listen, if they-- if you see they open that, we're going to jump in the lake.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You stay with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even if you can't swim, it's better to die in the lake than to die in there, in that oven.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we stayed there for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they kept opening up that, the oven and making it work, and closing it on purpose to frighten us, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So anyway, around-- I would say maybe 4 o'clock-- it was late, 4 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here we started to move a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were so glad to get away from that cremator-- crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we started to walk and walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then along the lake, there were all the officers' homes were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Beautiful homes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they walked us near the lake in front of their homes there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, there was a little road that went up to Furstenberg, to the village of Furstenberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the only nice-- the only nice thing we had when we were being counted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When it was a nice day, we could hear the bells of the church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they brought us up there, and we could-- we had to stand there a long time.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
